# CHANGELOG – World-Class PRD Builder (Evidence-Based)

## [v0.1.1] – 2025-09-08
### Added
- PRD section template for **KPIs & Success Metrics** (Markdown table format).
- Example JSON schema for product features with priority + dependencies.
### Changed
- Updated RACI matrix structure (simplified roles: R/A/C/I only).
### Notes
- מחזק את היכולת להפיק PRD שימושי תוך ≤1 שעה.
- נותן פורמט אחיד שקל להעתיק ל־Notion או Google Docs.

## [v0.1.0] – 2025-09-07
### Added
- Initial backup created with `instructions.md`, `gpt-meta.json`, `custom_gpt_200_qa.md`.
- Role defined as **Evidence-based PRD generator**.
- Supports JSON schema, KPIs, RACI, rubric scoring.
- Boundaries: evidence-based only, requires sources.

### Notes
- Serves as PRD backbone; first committed backup.
